sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>Configurable/HTTPS
    participant Provider as Garak Provider<br/>(Plugin)
    participant Files as Files API<br/>(Llama Stack)
    participant Garak as Garak Subprocess<br/>(Local)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LLM as Target LLM<br/>(Under Test)
    participant Safety as Safety API<br/>(Llama Stack)
    participant Inference as Inference API<br/>(Llama Stack)

    Note over Client, LLM: Flow 1: Inline Scan Lifecycle

    Client->>LLS: POST run_eval()<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    LLS->>Provider: run_eval() dispatch
    Provider->>Files: Download benchmark config<br/>HTTP, API key
    Files-->>Provider: Scan configuration
    Provider->>Garak: Launch subprocess<br/>Process I/O
    Garak->>LLM: Adversarial prompts<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    LLM-->>Garak: Completions
    Garak-->>Provider: JSONL reports + AVID + hit logs
    Provider->>Provider: Parse results + TBSA scoring
    Provider->>Files: Upload reports<br/>HTTP, API key
    Provider-->>LLS: Job created (job_id)
    LLS-->>Client: EvaluateResponse<br/>HTTPS, TLS

    Note over Client, LLM: Flow 2: Remote (KFP) Scan Lifecycle

    Client->>LLS: POST run_eval()<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    LLS->>Provider: run_eval() dispatch (remote mode)
    Provider->>KFP: Submit 6-step pipeline<br/>HTTPS, TLS, Bearer token
    KFP-->>Provider: Pipeline run ID
    Note right of KFP: KFP Pipeline Execution
    KFP->>Files: Download scan config<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    KFP->>Garak: garak_scan step
    Garak->>LLM: Adversarial prompts<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    LLM-->>Garak: Completions
    KFP->>Files: Upload parsed results<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    loop Poll status
        Provider->>KFP: Get run status<br/>HTTPS, TLS, Bearer token
        KFP-->>Provider: Status (in_progress/completed)
    end
    Provider->>Files: Retrieve results<br/>HTTP, API key
    Provider-->>LLS: EvaluateResponse
    LLS-->>Client: Results<br/>HTTPS, TLS

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 3: EvalHub KFP Scan Lifecycle

    Note left of Provider: EvalHub Platform triggers<br/>GarakAdapter (K8s Job)
    Provider->>KFP: Submit pipeline<br/>HTTPS, TLS, Bearer token
    KFP->>S3: Download scan config<br/>HTTPS, TLS, AWS IAM
    KFP->>Garak: garak_scan step
    Garak->>LLM: Adversarial prompts<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    LLM-->>Garak: Completions
    KFP->>S3: Upload results<br/>HTTPS, TLS, AWS IAM
    Provider->>S3: Download results<br/>HTTPS, TLS, AWS IAM
    Note left of Provider: Report to EvalHub callbacks

    Note over Garak, Safety: Flow 4: Shield Scan (SimpleShieldOrchestrator)

    Garak->>Provider: Adversarial prompt<br/>Function call (local)
    Provider->>Safety: Input shield check<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    Safety-->>Provider: Shield result (pass/violation)
    Provider->>Inference: LLM call<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    Inference-->>Provider: LLM response
    Provider->>Safety: Output shield check<br/>HTTPS, TLS, API key
    Safety-->>Provider: Shield result (pass/violation)
    Provider-->>Garak: Response + violations<br/>Function call (local)
